snippet: Tim Tebow’s potentially valuable role with the Jets became clearer, but little else could be drawn from the team’s preseason loss to the Bengals.
abstract: New York Jets lose to the Cincinnati Bengals, 17-6, in their preseason opener.
lead_paragraph: Tim Tebow’s potentially valuable role with the Jets became clearer, but little else could be drawn from the team’s preseason loss to the Bengals.

headline.seo: Tebow and Sanchez Share Time as Jets Fall to Bengals
headline.main: In Opener, Jets Unveil Instead of Unleash
